OL,3,CFirst Minister rules out 15% rates
OL,4,Cincrease for Northern Ireland
OL,6,FStormont First Minister Michelle
OL,7,FO'Neill has ruled out increasing the
OL,8,Fregional rate in Northern Ireland by
OL,9,F15%.
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,12,FPengelly added it was the wrong time
OL,13,Fto be proposing revenue raising
OL,14,Fmeasures amid a back and forth between
OL,15,FBelfast and London over funding for
OL,16,Fthe re-established devolved government.
OL,18,FThe ministers were speaking during a
OL,19,Fvisit to the Shankill Women's Centre
OL,20,Fin Belfast.
