OL,6,FThey earlier visited the Ashton Centre
OL,7,Fand described developing childcare
OL,8,Fsupport as a key priority for the new
OL,9,FExecutive.
OL,11,FThe Treasury has offered to write off
OL,12,Falmost #600 million of Stormont debt,
OL,13,Fconditional on the Executive raising
OL,14,F#113 million ` the equivalent of a 15%
OL,15,Fregional rate increase ` and producing
OL,16,Fa plan to deliver sustainable finances.
