OL,3,CFirst Minister rules out 15% rates
OL,4,Cincrease for Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe stipulation is a key element of a
OL,7,F#3.3 billion financial package drawn
OL,8,Fup by the Government to support the
OL,9,Freturn of devolution in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,13,FArchibald said she has "serious
OL,14,Fconcerns" over the details published
OL,15,Fby the Treasury and had asked for an
OL,16,Furgent meeting.
OL,18,FMs O'Neill stated to media: "I am
OL,19,Fruling out a 15% rates increase".
