OL,3,CFirst Minister rules out 15% rates
OL,4,Cincrease for Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAsked whether the Executive is being
OL,7,Frealistic over its finances, Ms
OL,8,FO'Neill responded: "This isn't about
OL,9,Fus having a begging bowl approach, or
OL,10,Fthis isn't about us failing to
OL,11,Frecognise that perhaps there are
OL,12,Fthings that we can do differently, and
OL,13,Fthere are efficiencies to be found `
OL,14,Fwe're up for all of that.
OL,16,F"But I think on one hand for it to be
OL,17,Frecognised that we're under funded,
OL,18,Fand on the other hand to say we need
OL,19,Fto burden households who are really
OL,20,Fstruggling right now with further
OL,21,Fcosts isn't acceptable.
