OL,3,CFirst Minister rules out 15% rates
OL,4,Cincrease for Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"We're going to have these Treasury
OL,7,Fdiscussions. This is going to continue
OL,8,Finto the days and weeks ahead."
OL,10,FMs Little-Pengelly said they want
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland to be sustainable.
OL,13,F"There will be difficult decisions to
OL,14,Fbe made in the future in terms of
OL,15,Freform, and we're absolutely up for
OL,16,Fthat reform that is needed to be
OL,17,Fdone," she said.
