OL,3,CFirst Minister rules out 15% rates
OL,4,Cincrease for Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"But the reality of it is this, we
OL,7,Fhave huge numbers of families in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland that are in that
OL,9,Fsqueezed middle, we listen to them all
OL,10,Fthe time in terms of unaffordable
OL,11,Fchildcare pressures and inflation
OL,12,Fpressures which are really making life
OL,13,Fmore difficult for them.
OL,15,F"What is the narrative across the rest
OL,16,Fof the UK, it's all about trying to
OL,17,Fprotect household incomes, they're
OL,18,Feven talking about tax reductions, and
OL,19,Fyet in Northern Ireland we're being
OL,20,Fasked to increase the tax burden on
OL,21,Fthese hard-working families.
