OL,6,F"That is something that we're
OL,7,Fabsolutely joint on in terms of making
OL,8,Fthose representations to the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment and to the Secretary of
OL,10,FState that this is absolutely not the
OL,11,Fright time to be doing that.
OL,13,F"We need to be supporting those
OL,14,Ffamilies in relation to the pressure
OL,15,Fthey're under rather than adding to
OL,16,Ftheir pressures."
